The '''Trans-Galactic Gaming Enterprise Corporation''' was a largely successful company concerned with the [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]] business. They maintained a variety of game halls and casinos on a variety of worlds. It was apparently unrestricted by the reign of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] as the corporation was still active during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Period]].

